TITLE: Incorrect Default Locale Retrieval in Liferay Upgrade Java
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the incorrect approach of using `LocaleUtil.getDefault()` within a Liferay upgrade class. This method should be avoided because the thread locale might not be initialized during the upgrade process, leading to incorrect locale values.
