TITLE: Corrected Parentheses Usage in If-Statements - Java
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the preferred syntax for properly grouped relational expressions in Java if-statements using parentheses, ensuring clear evaluation order and adherence to coding standards. The "a" and "b" variables are compared to zero and properly grouped with OR.
SOURCE: https://github.com/liferay/liferay-portal/blob/master/modules/util/source-formatter/src/main/resources/documentation/check/if_statement_check.markdown#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: Java
