TITLE: Applying App Javadoc Builder Plugin in Gradle
DESCRIPTION: This Gradle build script snippet demonstrates how to apply the Liferay App Javadoc Builder plugin to the root project. It involves adding the plugin dependency (`com.liferay.gradle.plugins.app.javadoc.builder`) to the buildscript classpath from the specified Liferay Nexus repository and then applying the plugin using its ID `com.liferay.app.javadoc.builder`. This is the initial setup required to use the plugin's features.
