TITLE: Declaring Variables Stepwise without Chaining in Java
DESCRIPTION: This Java snippet demonstrates the preferred approach, declaring each intermediate result as its own variable. It uses UserLocalServiceUtil to retrieve a User object, extracts their first name, and transforms it to lowercase in separate statements. This improves clarity and allows for easier debugging and expansion. Required dependency: UserLocalServiceUtil from Liferay.
