TITLE: Correct Default Locale Retrieval in Java Upgrade Classes
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows the correct method for retrieving the default locale in Liferay Portal upgrade classes. It uses UpgradeProcessUtil to get the default language ID and then converts it to a Locale object using LocaleUtil.
SOURCE: https://github.com/liferay/liferay-portal/blob/master/modules/util/source-formatter/documentation/upgrade_locale_util.markdown#2025-04-22_snippet_1

