TITLE: Correctly Loading Resource Bundle using Liferay ResourceBundleLoader (Java)
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates the Liferay-recommended approach using `ResourceBundleLoader.loadResourceBundle` to correctly load resource bundles, ensuring proper UTF-8 encoding is handled regardless of the default platform encoding. It also uses `ResourceBundleUtil.getString` for safe retrieval of localized strings. This method requires obtaining an instance of `ResourceBundleLoader` (e.g., via dependency injection or a service lookup, represented here by `getResourceBundleLoader()`).
