TITLE: Creating and Traversing RDF Models with Apache Jena
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates how to create an RDF Model and traverse through its statements (triples). It extracts and processes the subject, predicate, and object from each statement, which are fundamental components of RDF data structures.
SOURCE: https://github.com/liferay/liferay-portal/blob/master/modules/apps/blogs/blogs-demo-data-creator-impl/src/main/resources/com/liferay/blogs/demo/data/creator/internal/dependencies/creative/commons/subtitle_5.txt#2025-04-22_snippet_0

