SOURCE: https://github.com/liferay/liferay-portal/blob/master/portal-web/test/functional/com/liferay/portalweb/tests/enduser/collaboration/knowledgebase/dependencies/KBArticlesWithMetadata.zip/articles/adt/knowledge-base-article-parent-title-1-child-1.markdown#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: jsp
