TITLE: Discouraged Pattern: Nested Conditional Logic in Instance Initializer
DESCRIPTION: Shows the discouraged approach of nesting conditional logic within an instance initializer. This pattern creates unnecessary nesting and separates related logical conditions that should be evaluated together.
SOURCE: https://github.com/liferay/liferay-portal/blob/master/modules/util/source-formatter/src/main/resources/documentation/check/instance_initializer_check.markdown#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
private ObjectDefinition _toObjectDefinition(
    com.liferay.object.model.ObjectDefinition objectDefinition) {

    return new ObjectDefinition() {
        {
            if (FeatureFlagManagerUtil.isEnabled("LPD-34594")) {
                setRootObjectDefinitionExternalReferenceCode(
                    () -> {
                        if (!objectDefinition.isSystem()) {
                            return null;
                        }

                        return objectDefinition.getExternalReferenceCode();
                    });
            }
        }
    };
}
```

