TITLE: Subqueries and Complex Operations
DESCRIPTION: Complex SQL queries using subqueries, derived tables, and UNION operations
SOURCE: https://github.com/liferay/liferay-portal/blob/master/portal-impl/test/unit/com/liferay/portal/dao/orm/hibernate/dependencies/sql.txt#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT * FROM A INNER JOIN (SELECT * FROM B) b ON A.a = b.a#A,B
```

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT * FROM A UNION SELECT * FROM B#A,B
```

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT * FROM (SELECT * FROM A)#A
```

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT * FROM (SELECT * FROM A) A#A
```

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT * FROM (SELECT * FROM A) INNER JOIN B ON A.a = B.b#A,B
```

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT * FROM (SELECT * FROM A) INNER JOIN B ON A.a = B.b UNION SELECT * FROM (SELECT * FROM C) INNER JOIN D ON C.c = D.d#A,B,C,D
```

