SOURCE: https://github.com/liferay/liferay-portal/blob/master/portal-web/test/functional/com/liferay/portalweb/tests/enduser/collaboration/knowledgebase/dependencies/KBArticlesWithMarkdown.zip/articles/02-KB-Parent-3/01-KB-Parent-3-Child-1.markdown#2025-04-22_snippet_6

