TITLE: Replacing AND Operator in SQL String - Liferay CustomSQL - Java
DESCRIPTION: Replaces logical AND operators in a SQL string with either "AND" or "OR", based on a boolean parameter. This aids in dynamic query construction involving conditional logic. Accepts a SQL string and a boolean flag (true for AND, false for OR), returning the modified SQL. Assumes proper escaping for SQL syntax and should be used carefully to avoid logic errors.
SOURCE: https://github.com/liferay/liferay-portal/blob/master/modules/apps/portal-workflow/portal-workflow-kaleo-service/find-security-bugs-false-positives.txt#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
public String replaceAndOperator(String sql, boolean andOperator) {
    // Replaces the logical AND/OR operator in the SQL string based on the flag
    return sql.replace("[$AND_OR_CONNECTOR$]", andOperator ? "AND" : "OR");
}
```

